data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER! This 4-bedroom 2912 sq ft home nestled on a sprawling 1.15-acre lot offers so much! The heart of the house, the expansive kitchen, beckons with its generous proportions, promising culinary adventures and gatherings. 
Enter through the beautiful foyer, you will be enchanted by the charm. The enclosed front porch invites you curl up and read and to have lots of houseplants, while the dining room is ready to host countless memorable meals.  The first floor also has a room currently used as an office that could be a 5th bed. Two living rooms one features coziness with a brick wall and wood burner for winter evenings, while the other feels more formal and welcomes natural light 

Outside, the possibilities are endless. Explore the outbuildings that could be perfect for hobbies or storage. The gazebo and courtyard hold the potential to become enchanting outdoor retreats. You have over an acre to plant a garden and create your own homestead. There is a deck just off gazebo. an area for firepit with some downed wood. 

This property, awaiting your vision, is a canvas of opportunity. Updates include new windows and sliding glass door 2020, septic 2019, furnace 2018 and updated electric wiring and boxes in house and garage. A  fresh coat of paint or siding will help restore its grandeur. Above the 2 car garage is an apartment that with some TLC could be income producing. Embrace the potential and make this house your own. 
Easy drive to Zanesville, Newark, Coshocton & New Albany
